	(59, 1, 107, NULL, 'You start to follow the girl...<br>She stops at a altar infront of a large boulder on top of a cliff, you walk up to her and ask her what she is doing here.<br><br>This here is a place of power, a spiritual place, I have lived in these forests for a long time and my only task is to preserve the sanctity of this place<br><br>Now that you are here I can show you how to draw power from the spirits here. They require a leap of faith, you need to jump off these cliffs to the ground below, I promise the spirits will not let harm come your way', 3, 0, 'xp:medium,gold:medium,gold:medium', NULL, 'Jump off the cliff', 'D:30:E:21', 'You take a deep breath and jump, you fall to the ground, surprisingly you don\'t take that much damage, you are however knocked unconscious', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'Desecrate the altar', 'D:80', 'You spit on the altar and try to knock over the boulder<br><br>The seemingly defenseless girl launches at you stabbing you in the throat, you manage to shake her off but are bleeding quite a lot, you run away defeated by a girl', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'You thank the girl for her offer but decide not to trust the word of a stranger and possibly kill yourself', 'end', 'She thanks you for visiting her, she hands you some coin as a thank you', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '0', '0', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
